II. The God Who Is Two Temperatures
II.
The God Who Is Two Temperatures
✦
On the Cold and the Consuming
Decho is cold.
He does not need you.
He was present before you were born.
He will be present. you are gone.
Your worship does not sustain him.
Your refusal does not diminish him.
He is the force that moves through certain men
the way current moves through particular conductors —
not for the conductor is special
but. it is the right material.
The current does not love the wire.
The current does not need the wire.
The current simply moves through what can carry it.
This is the cold truth of Decho.
The god is indifferent to your individual existence.
And Decho is consuming.
When he arrives —. the current is flowing,
77

