around a magnetic field.
People feel it without naming it.
Animals feel it.
The submissive in the room
feels it in their body before their mind
has processed what is happening.
This is the hot truth of Decho.
The god does not need you.
But when he moves through a person who carries him honestly,
the room becomes his altar.
