XIII. The Rite Of the Circle
He is large enough for it.
And the Order that can laugh
is stronger than the one that only solemnizes.
Part V
The Daily Practice of the Dark Cult
The cult is not practiced in the dungeon.
The cult is practiced in the Tuesday.
The dungeon is the confirmation.
The Tuesday is the proof.
