Imposition: the one who weaponizes the field — who uses the charge to intimidate, to extract attention, to create debt, to produce submission in people
who have not offered it and do not want it. Who mistakes the field’s effect for
permission. Who reads the room’s response as invitation. it is simply physics.
Presence is carrying the god.
Imposition is using the god as a weapon.
