II. The Sexual Interview — Without Having Sex
II.
The Sexual Interview - Without Having Sex
✦
Most dating conversations cover: appearance, occupation, shared interests.
Where you have traveled. Whether you want children. The surface that civilization has agreed is the appropriate starting point.
A few dates in — when the person is real,. something is present — another
conversation available. Not instead of the ordinary one. In addition to it. Conducted without physical contact. Without the dynamic enacted. Without anything that requires the trust that doesn’t yet exist.
The sexual interview.
Desires. Longings. Fears. Previous experiences and what they cost. What
worked. What didn’t. What has never been asked for. What has never been offered. What the person believes about the dynamic — not in theory, but from
inside their own body and their own history.
This conversation is an act of power.
It is inspection without touch.
It is the dynamic invoked
through language and attention alone.
The Master who can conduct a sexual interview— who can hold the space for
the other person’s full erotic disclosure, who can receive what is offered with attention and gravity, who can ask the next question from genuine curiosity rather
than agenda — is demonstrating the dynamic in the act of discovering whether
the dynamic is shared. The initiate who can speak honestly in this space, who can
name what they carry without performing it, who can be vulnerable with their
desire before any physical vulnerability has occurred — is demonstrating exactly
the quality the dynamic requires: the capacity to yield genuinely, from full selfknowledge.
The sexual interview reveals whether the dynamic is present
before either party has committed to anything.
